tests.title: I can see Military Service Obligation text
tests.fullTitle: Active Army Student Applies for Bachelor Ed Goal and Funding I can see Military Service Obligation text
tests.code:
cy.contains('I acknowledge (Commissioned Officers, CW2/2LT & up) that I incur a Military Service Obligation (MSO) IAW Title 10 USC, Section 2007. As a regular Army, Active Guard and Reserve, or Title 10/Title 32 mobilized Officer, I acknowledge that I incur an Active Duty Service Obligation (ADSO) of two years. As a Reserve Component (USAR/ARNG) officer, I acknowledge that I incur a Reserve Duty Service Obligation (RDSO) of four years. The TA MSO begins on the ending term date of each class for which TA was approved. I understand that I may not under any circumstances reimburse an institution or a TA-funded class to avoid an MSO. Only the Secretary of the Army or designee may waive my TA-imposed MSO; if waived, I am subject to recoupment of TA.');
cy.wait(2000);
